stackFileContent:
version: '2.1'
networks:
    portainer_internal:
      external: true
services:
  develop:
    image: saile2204/kassensystem-bbs2-wob:latest-develop
    environment:
      - PUID=1000
      - PGID=1000
      - TZ=Etc/UTC
      - ConnectionString=Server=HOST;Database=DATABASE;Uid=USER;Pwd=PASSWORD
    networks:
      - portainer_internal
    restart: unless-stopped
